      "description": "This vehicle is in good, solid condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior looks great overall, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable; the upholstery is in great shape with no tears, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster and steering wheel. Mechanically, it runs beautifully with a smooth engine and transmission, and all electronics are fully functional. It's a reliable, attractive car that offers a great balance of quality and value.",
