    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system to reach an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels through a factory M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis is exceptional; the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with original bushings and dampers in peak condition. The interior is pristine, featuring Nappa leather with no bolster wear and a perfect instrument cluster. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
